<p>with (possibly empty) Dyck words <span class="texhtml"><i>w</i><sub>1</sub></span> and <span class="texhtml"><i>w</i><sub>2</sub></span>.
</p><p>The <a href="/wiki/Generating_function" title="Generating function">generating function</a> for the Catalan numbers is defined by
