However, other combinatorial descriptions are only known<sup id="cite&#95;ref-Chen2012&#95;17-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Chen2012-17"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>17<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup>
for <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle m=2,3}">
